Package projecttwo

Class Student

  • java.lang.Object
    • projecttwo.Student
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Student>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    International, NonResident, Resident
    public abstract class Student
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Student>
    This is an abstract class that represents a student. Each student has a profile, major, and number of credits completed. All students also have some amount of tuition due.
    Author:
    Aryan Jairath, Anis Chihoub
